    "how_to_trigger": "Repro steps:First use Debug Book: Go to region > Act 1 > UND - Underdark > Fearful RotheSeveral variations in dialogue depending on what player does from here:Variation 1: Use roll amazing. Walk towards the nearby Rothe to trigger a conversation with Skarjall.  Pick 1 > 2. Then talk to the Rothe. Pick 2 and roll the dice.Variation 2: Use roll amazing. Walk towards the nearby Rothe to trigger a conversation with Skarjall.  Pick 1 > 1 > 1, roll dice, then Pick 1. Next talk to the Rothe. Pick 2 and roll dice.Variation 3: Walk towards the nearby Rothe to trigger a conversation with Skarjall.  Pick Leave. Then Ctrl+Shift+K on the Cave-In (the rubble behind the Rothe)."
